# go-voyageai

[![Go Reference](https://pkg.go.dev/badge/github.com/conneroisu/go-voyageai.svg)](https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/conneroisu/go-voyageai)
[<img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Phorm-Ask_AI-%23F2777A.svg?&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64," />](https://www.phorm.ai/query?projectId=01ae7808-fdc2-4cd5-a2f6-4a4c0e614fc7)

Unofficial go client for [ voyage ai ](https://www.voyageai.com/).

## Installation

```bash
go get github.com/conneroisu/go-voyageai
```

## Usage

```go
package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"log"

	"github.com/conneroisu/go-voyageai"
)

func main() {
	// create a new client
	client := voyageai.NewClient("YOUR_API_KEY")
	// create a new embedding request
	req := voyageai.EmbeddingsRequest{
		Model: string(voyageai.VoyageLarge2Instruct),
		Input: []string{"Hello, world!"},
	}
	// make the request
	res, err := client.Embeddings(req)
	if err != nil {
		log.Fatal(err)
	}
	// print the response is of type EmbeddingsResponse
	fmt.Println(res)
}
```
